comment_data.body: I think that in cases like these, we should not be reporting them as exceptions. Depending on the situation, we should either silently ignore them (if the action was not triggered by a user), or do something subtle, like reporting the issue as a temporary toast in the status line.

rename.to: don't report some flutter_tools errors as exceptions
